name: i asked my neural net if i were happy
description:
i programmed a convolutional neural network to understand human emotions. she is pretty good at it. her filters help her to see an image from several points of view, and to recognize the emotion.

this is what she sees when i give her a picture of me. 24 layers to understand my emotions. 24 layers to understand if her creator is happy, angry, in pain.

i don't know what i feel, but she says i am sad.
